### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/info

### 获取模板配置
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/template-config

### 获取临时 Token
POST http://localhost:25052/api/v1/auth/api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 使用 Bearer Token 访问受保护的接口
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE

### 创建持久化 APIKEY
POST http://localhost:25052/api/v1/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My API Key"
}

### 使用 APIKEY 访问受保护的接口
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/api-keys
X-API-Key: YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

### ========================================
### Creatomate API 代理接口
### 路径格式：/creatomate/{version}/{path}
### ========================================

### 获取 Creatomate 模板列表
# 实际转发到: GET https://api.creatomate.com/v1/templates
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/creatomate/v1/templates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE

### 获取渲染列表（带分页）
# 实际转发到: GET https://api.creatomate.com/v1/renders
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/creatomate/v1/renders?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE

### 创建视频渲染任务（使用模板）
# 实际转发到: POST https://api.creatomate.com/v1/renders
POST http://localhost:25052/api/v1/creatomate/v1/renders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template_id": "c937d125-b99b-4690-96f0-6aa1f09438c9",
  "modifications": {
    "Text-1": "Hello World"
  }
}

### 创建视频渲染任务（自定义渲染）
# 实际转发到: POST https://api.creatomate.com/v1/renders
POST http://localhost:25052/api/v1/creatomate/v1/renders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "output_format": "mp4",
  "width": 1280,
  "height": 720,
  "duration": 3,
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "My first video generated with RenderScript!",
      "fill_color": "#ff0000",
      "width": "50%",
      "height": "25%"
    }
  ]
}

### 获取指定渲染任务详情
# 实际转发到: GET https://api.creatomate.com/v1/renders/{renderId}
# 请将 {renderId} 替换为实际的渲染任务 ID
GET http://localhost:25052/api/v1/creatomate/v1/renders/d8e2f891-3c4a-4b5c-8d7e-1f2a3b4c5d6e
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_KEY_HERE
